<i>adverb</i>: 풀풀 [풀풀], 폴폴 [폴폴] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>풀풀 [풀풀]</dt><br>
<dd>1. thickly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 먼지나 연기 등이 몹시 흩날리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing snow, dust, smoke, etc., fluttering much.</dd><br>
<dd>2. jumpily</dd><br>
<dd>빠르고 힘이 넘치는 듯이 자꾸 뛰거나 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing someone or something repeatedly jumping or flying fast and powerfully.</dd><br>
<dd>3. hard</dd><br>
<dd>물이 심하게 끓어오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing water boiling rapidly.</dd><br>
<dd>4. with a scent</dd><br>
<dd>냄새 등이 심하게 자꾸 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a smell, etc., giving off a strong and continuous smell.</dd><br>
<dt>폴폴 [폴폴]</dt><br>
<dd>1. thickly</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 먼지, 연기 등이 흩날리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing snow, dust, smoke, etc., fluttering.</dd><br>
<dd>2. jumpily</dd><br>
<dd>동작이 빠르고 힘이 넘치는 듯이 자꾸 뛰거나 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one's moving fast and jumping or flying fast and powerfully.</dd><br>
<dd>3. hard</dd><br>
<dd>적은 물이 자꾸 끓어오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a small amount of water boiling continuously.</dd><br>
<dd>4. with a scent</dd><br>
<dd>냄새가 자꾸 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a smell, etc., continuing to smell.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>